1
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:41,020
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,060 --> 00:01:43,990
[Episode 15]

3
00:01:49,780 --> 00:01:50,479
Serving chopsticks.

4
00:01:50,479 --> 00:01:50,950
Get another pair.

5
00:01:50,950 --> 00:01:53,009
Don't bump into it when turning this.

6
00:01:54,070 --> 00:01:54,729
Over here.

7
00:01:55,039 --> 00:01:55,950
Hurry up.

8
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:57,430
Put one here,

9
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,280
and put one here.

10
00:01:58,280 --> 00:02:00,340
Don't bump into it when turning this.

11
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:02,630
[February 5 Wednesday 14:45]

12
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:05,100
Chef Jia took more than
half the kitchen staff with him.

13
00:02:05,100 --> 00:02:05,830
I need staff.

14
00:02:06,550 --> 00:02:07,470
How many do you need?

15
00:02:07,470 --> 00:02:08,490
I want 3 sous chefs,

16
00:02:08,490 --> 00:02:09,550
and a dessert chef.

17
00:02:10,169 --> 00:02:11,360
I can't give you 3.

18
00:02:11,390 --> 00:02:12,380
I'll give you 1 first.

19
00:02:12,380 --> 00:02:15,380
I'll transfer the rest to you
from other departments.

20
00:02:15,550 --> 00:02:15,990
Okay.

21
00:02:16,470 --> 00:02:17,870
Mr. Ji, Mr. Xue.

22
00:02:18,250 --> 00:02:18,810
What is it?

23
00:02:18,810 --> 00:02:21,280
I just went to Manager Chen of purchasing

24
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:23,280
to have him sign
the guests' dietary restriction list.

25
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:25,740
I happened to see him
lock the door and leave,

26
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,570
so I came to ask what is going on.

27
00:02:28,190 --> 00:02:28,710
Got it.

28
00:02:29,420 --> 00:02:30,430
As for people from other departments,

29
00:02:30,430 --> 00:02:31,280
I want Xu Miyu.

30
00:02:31,300 --> 00:02:33,430
You can arrange the rest as you see fit.

31
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:35,870
Ms. Xu,

32
00:02:35,940 --> 00:02:37,910
our kitchen is understaffed right now.

33
00:02:37,910 --> 00:02:38,840
Are you willing

34
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,680
to stay and help Chef Li?

35
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:43,450
I am.

36
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:45,430
Great.

37
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:46,220
And me.

38
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:47,480
I can help too.

39
00:02:48,070 --> 00:02:48,770
You?

40
00:02:49,190 --> 00:02:50,280
I can cook.

41
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:52,400
I made the 8 cold dishes and 8 hot dishes

42
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,840
for our family's New Year's Eve dinner.

43
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:54,590
Then Chef Li,

44
00:02:54,590 --> 00:02:55,910
you decide this.

45
00:02:56,630 --> 00:02:57,890
Where is the sous chef?

46
00:02:58,590 --> 00:02:59,280
Here.

47
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:00,470
Come here.

48
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:04,460
I am Guo Luda.

49
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,750
Okay, Mr. Guo.

50
00:03:05,750 --> 00:03:07,190
Today you are responsible
for reading the orders

51
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:08,080
and serving the food.

52
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,910
The banquet hall and the Chinese
restaurant must be separated.

53
00:03:09,910 --> 00:03:11,510
You can't make any mistakes.

54
00:03:11,910 --> 00:03:12,560
Okay, no problem.

55
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,240
Okay.

56
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:14,820
It's 3:10 now.

57
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,530
Let's begin.

58
00:03:18,150 --> 00:03:19,270
Come on, hurry up.

59
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:22,400
Find someone to open the office.

60
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:22,930
Okay.

61
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:40,910
Darn it.

62
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,960
Chen ran off with Jia Shikun.

63
00:03:44,590 --> 00:03:46,280
I never thought about

64
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:48,880
getting anything
from them in the first place.

65
00:03:50,190 --> 00:03:52,750
But now they've made things look so ugly.

66
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:55,780
[Staff Personal Health Standard]

67
00:03:58,190 --> 00:04:00,240
The troubles facing the Chinese restaurant

68
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:02,240
may be worse than I imagined.

69
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:17,480
Prepare some flour and minced meat for me.

70
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,620
Okay. How much meat?

71
00:04:18,950 --> 00:04:19,560
1.5 kg?

72
00:04:19,870 --> 00:04:20,430
2.5?

73
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:21,950
2.5 kg.

74
00:04:23,190 --> 00:04:24,510
Then slice some sweet potatoes,

75
00:04:24,510 --> 00:04:25,720
along with perilla leaves and eggplant.

76
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:26,680
Make all the slices a bit thick.

77
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,510
Hurry up.

78
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:28,000
Okay.

79
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,190
We're still short-handed.

80
00:04:32,190 --> 00:04:33,790
Find some more people for me.

81
00:04:39,830 --> 00:04:40,560
All washed?

82
00:04:41,430 --> 00:04:43,270
Do you know how to peel tomatoes?

83
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,310
Peel them?

84
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,920
Okay, I'll do it.

85
00:04:51,510 --> 00:04:52,870
I'd better do it.

86
00:04:53,190 --> 00:04:54,290
Didn't she say we're short-handed?

87
00:04:54,290 --> 00:04:55,190
Let me do it.

88
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,500
Why don't you try this?

89
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:01,190
Okay.

90
00:05:02,070 --> 00:05:05,720
Just score a cross at the top.

91
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:13,370
Then put it in boiling water.

92
00:05:14,610 --> 00:05:16,150
Then the skin will split open.

93
00:05:16,150 --> 00:05:16,680
Try it.

94
00:05:16,700 --> 00:05:17,330
Okay.

95
00:05:32,430 --> 00:05:33,240
It didn't burn you, did it?

96
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:33,920
I'm fine.

97
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:36,600
You have to slide the tomatoes

98
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:38,040
down the side of the pot.

99
00:05:38,210 --> 00:05:39,430
Don't just drop them in from the top.

100
00:05:39,430 --> 00:05:42,030
Otherwise, the splashing water
will burn you.

101
00:05:42,159 --> 00:05:43,090
Let me try again.

102
00:06:10,370 --> 00:06:11,350
Here it comes.

103
00:06:11,870 --> 00:06:12,930
Careful, it's hot.

104
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,570
Looks and smells great.

105
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,720
How does it taste?

106
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:21,120
It's time.

107
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:28,150
Guys, it's 5:00.

108
00:06:28,330 --> 00:06:29,120
Hurry up.

109
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:31,590
Dinner in the banquet hall
starts promptly at 6:30.

110
00:06:31,590 --> 00:06:33,590
Let's hurry up, guys! Come on!

111
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:47,590
You'd better go help Mr. Ji.

112
00:06:53,870 --> 00:06:54,510
Mr. Ji.

113
00:06:54,810 --> 00:06:55,909
I'll take over.

114
00:06:56,020 --> 00:06:57,360
You go greet the guests.

115
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:02,930
Okay, I'll leave the rest to you.

116
00:07:03,390 --> 00:07:04,120
Give it to me.

117
00:07:06,780 --> 00:07:08,070
I put your suit

118
00:07:08,070 --> 00:07:09,040
in the kitchen office.

119
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:11,040
I was afraid it might get dirty here.

120
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,400
Thank you.

121
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:24,870
Thank you for coming all this way.

122
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:25,560
Not at all.

123
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:27,380
You can go over there first.

124
00:07:27,630 --> 00:07:28,960
Please, right this way.

125
00:07:30,830 --> 00:07:31,600
Kenny.

126
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:33,810
Marcos.

127
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,430
We meet again.

128
00:07:35,430 --> 00:07:36,220
Yes.

129
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,240
Let me make an introduction.

130
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:39,680
This is the Commercial Director
of Puqi Group.

131
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,430
Mr. Cheng.

132
00:07:40,430 --> 00:07:41,460
Mr. Cheng, this is

133
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:43,450
Mr. Ji Feng, General Manager
of Purong Hotel.

134
00:07:43,450 --> 00:07:44,380
Nice to meet you.

135
00:07:44,430 --> 00:07:45,560
Nice to meet you, too, Mr. Cheng.

136
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:47,000
We have your table ready.

137
00:07:48,030 --> 00:07:49,490
Sorry to keep you waiting.

138
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:52,350
We've prepared an appetizer for you.

139
00:07:50,810 --> 00:07:53,310
[All staff of Purong Hotel]

140
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:55,800
I believe it's a dish
you're very familiar with.

141
00:07:53,330 --> 00:07:56,500
[warmly welcome Mr. Marcos]

142
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:56,430
Thank you.

143
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:59,060
[We will serve you sincerely]

144
00:07:59,870 --> 00:08:00,720
Okay.

145
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:04,160
This is a Spanish cold soup.

146
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,570
Enjoy your meal, everyone.

147
00:08:18,140 --> 00:08:18,920
I'm serious.

148
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,730
This tastes exactly

149
00:08:20,950 --> 00:08:23,830
the same
as what I had in Cordoba.

150
00:08:24,510 --> 00:08:25,150
Really?

151
00:08:25,180 --> 00:08:26,180
You should try it.

152
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:31,040
That's something.

153
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:32,240
Thank you.

154
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,289
Enjoy.

155
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:36,600
Not bad.

156
00:08:38,789 --> 00:08:40,590
Next up are the Shanghai dishes.

157
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:41,510
Come on.

158
00:08:43,909 --> 00:08:44,790
Please enjoy.

159
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:57,490
This is exactly like
the kind I had as a kid,

160
00:08:57,510 --> 00:08:59,120
deep-fried dough sticks
made from sourdough.

161
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,790
Your hands would be
covered in oil after eating.

162
00:09:00,790 --> 00:09:02,150
It smelt so great.

163
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,840
It's a pity that nowadays,

164
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,270
you can't find
breakfast shops like this anymore.

165
00:09:05,270 --> 00:09:06,120
I see.

166
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,290
That's a pity.

167
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:10,150
Then we hope you

168
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:11,940
can come to our hotel
for breakfast more often, Mr. Cheng.

169
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:12,610
It's a deal.

170
00:09:13,510 --> 00:09:13,910
Mr. Cheng,

171
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:16,310
is it convenient for me
to add you on WeChat?

172
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:16,790
No problem.

173
00:09:16,790 --> 00:09:18,120
Come, add her on WeChat.

174
00:09:19,150 --> 00:09:20,150
What do you think?

175
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:21,030
It's fried quite well.

176
00:09:21,030 --> 00:09:21,550
Just right.

177
00:09:21,470 --> 00:09:22,160
[All staff of Purong Hotel]

178
00:09:21,550 --> 00:09:22,180
What do you think?

179
00:09:22,180 --> 00:09:22,880
[warmly welcome Mr. Marcos]

180
00:09:22,390 --> 00:09:22,840
You can scan my code.

181
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:23,720
It smells really great.

182
00:09:22,900 --> 00:09:23,590
[We will serve you sincerely]

183
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,030
The taste of childhood.

184
00:09:26,030 --> 00:09:26,730
Right?

185
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,370
Okay, got it.

186
00:09:30,740 --> 00:09:32,430
Are you satisfied with the dishes?

187
00:09:32,430 --> 00:09:33,370
Isn't it greasy?

188
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:35,080
If you feel it's too greasy,
some soy milk will help.

189
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,150
Enjoy your meal.

190
00:09:36,150 --> 00:09:37,880
It can relieve the greasiness.

191
00:09:49,030 --> 00:09:50,290
Eight-Treasure Duck.

192
00:09:50,390 --> 00:09:51,270
It's done.

193
00:09:53,040 --> 00:09:53,600
[Purong Hotel Chinese Restaurant; Dine-In;
Eight-Treasure Duck]

194
00:09:56,030 --> 00:09:58,430
Poached Shrimp, one, two, three.

195
00:09:58,630 --> 00:10:00,030
Seven plates of Poached Shrimp.

196
00:10:00,030 --> 00:10:00,630
No, eight...

197
00:10:00,630 --> 00:10:01,430
Eight plates.

198
00:10:01,630 --> 00:10:02,850
How many plates exactly?

199
00:10:02,850 --> 00:10:03,630
Don't worry about it.

200
00:10:03,630 --> 00:10:05,200
Start cooking first.
We'll plate whatever we get.

201
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,670
The guest would like to cancel
the Tofu with Crab Roe.

202
00:10:06,670 --> 00:10:07,870
Tofu with Crab Roe...

203
00:10:08,030 --> 00:10:10,030
This has garlic.
The guest wants it remade.

204
00:10:10,030 --> 00:10:11,830
So noisy.
My head’s about to explode.

205
00:10:11,830 --> 00:10:12,930
Put it there first.

206
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:15,370
And Stir-Fried Shrimp with Rice Wine.

207
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,700
-Is it done?
-Yes. Yes.

208
00:10:20,150 --> 00:10:20,910
Waiter,

209
00:10:20,910 --> 00:10:22,390
when will the dishes
for our table be served?

210
00:10:22,390 --> 00:10:24,000
We've been waiting
for nearly half an hour.

211
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:24,750
The kitchen is preparing.

212
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:25,270
It will be served right away.

213
00:10:25,270 --> 00:10:25,870
Please wait a moment.

214
00:10:25,870 --> 00:10:27,150
Hurry up.

215
00:10:27,510 --> 00:10:28,270
Waitor,

216
00:10:28,510 --> 00:10:29,630
we've finished our cold dishes.

217
00:10:29,630 --> 00:10:30,910
When will you serve us the hot dishes?

218
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:31,390
Right away.

219
00:10:31,390 --> 00:10:32,000
I'll go urge them now.

220
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:32,750
Hurry up.

221
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:40,790
Mr. Guo, you go inside and help.

222
00:10:40,790 --> 00:10:41,720
Leave this to me.

223
00:10:41,910 --> 00:10:42,330
Okay.

224
00:10:43,630 --> 00:10:44,630
Get me a fresh one.

225
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:45,670
Here.

226
00:10:52,630 --> 00:10:54,510
Six portions of Braised Wheat Gluten.

227
00:10:54,510 --> 00:10:55,120
Okay.

228
00:11:09,670 --> 00:11:10,750
Okay, go.

229
00:11:11,790 --> 00:11:12,750
Careful.

230
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:18,870
Is the Tempura ready?

231
00:11:18,870 --> 00:11:19,960
A bunch of idiots.

232
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,320
Hurry up, bro!

233
00:11:23,430 --> 00:11:24,200
Mr. Ji.

234
00:11:28,030 --> 00:11:28,790
Sorry, Mr. Ji.

235
00:11:28,790 --> 00:11:29,390
I was in such a hurry,

236
00:11:29,390 --> 00:11:30,510
I didn't recognize you.

237
00:11:30,510 --> 00:11:31,640
-It’s okay.
-Sorry.

238
00:11:31,670 --> 00:11:32,320
Mr. Ji,

239
00:11:32,510 --> 00:11:33,630
the large private room
in the Chinese restaurant

240
00:11:33,630 --> 00:11:35,240
just ordered 18 portions
of Hainanese Chicken Rice at once.

241
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,120
The staff were too quick.

242
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:37,840
They've already served all the chicken rice
meant for the banquet hall.

243
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:39,790
We might come up short here.

244
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:42,030
Chef Li, are there any other options?

245
00:11:42,030 --> 00:11:42,960
We can use the cooked rice

246
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,270
to make soy sauce fried rice.

247
00:11:44,270 --> 00:11:45,390
But it's too hard.

248
00:11:45,390 --> 00:11:46,270
It's not suitable for the final dish.

249
00:11:46,270 --> 00:11:47,730
How about making noodles?

250
00:11:47,910 --> 00:11:49,510
I'm afraid it's too late to make it now.

251
00:11:49,510 --> 00:11:50,670
What kind of noodles do you want to make?

252
00:11:50,670 --> 00:11:51,840
The guests have been eating

253
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:52,910
seafood and red meat all night.

254
00:11:52,910 --> 00:11:54,750
A bowl of plain noodles now

255
00:11:54,750 --> 00:11:56,040
would be refreshing
and cut through the grease.

256
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:58,030
It's good, but it lacks a gimmick.

257
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,790
We can make plain noodles in chicken soup.

258
00:12:00,790 --> 00:12:02,400
Chicken soup with mature hen
from Southern Anhui.

259
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:03,150
Since it's to cleanse the palate,

260
00:12:03,150 --> 00:12:04,280
it can't be too rich.

261
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,320
How about Fish Bone Soup
with Bamboo Leaves?

262
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,050
I can make it.

263
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:08,870
You'll make it.

264
00:12:08,870 --> 00:12:09,240
Okay.

265
00:12:09,550 --> 00:12:10,790
Chef Li, please keep
an eye on things here.

266
00:12:10,790 --> 00:12:11,550
I'll go outside and take a look.

267
00:12:11,550 --> 00:12:11,880
Okay.

268
00:12:12,030 --> 00:12:12,560
Let's go.

269
00:13:14,920 --> 00:13:15,450
Mr. Ji.

270
00:13:16,770 --> 00:13:17,590
Try some.

271
00:13:18,630 --> 00:13:19,270
I don't need this much.

272
00:13:19,270 --> 00:13:20,470
I'll just have a bite.

273
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:30,150
I haven't tasted it properly yet.

274
00:13:30,150 --> 00:13:31,550
Let me have another bite.

275
00:13:40,870 --> 00:13:41,550
Mr. Ji,

276
00:13:41,670 --> 00:13:43,130
this whole bowl is for you.

277
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:46,080
You've been too busy to eat all night.

278
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:48,280
Have some noodles to line your stomach.

279
00:13:50,260 --> 00:13:51,360
Okay, thank you.

280
00:14:01,270 --> 00:14:02,360
Who came up with this terrible idea

281
00:14:02,360 --> 00:14:04,420
to change the menu at the last minute?

282
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:05,680
What's going on?

283
00:14:11,510 --> 00:14:12,390
Xu Miyu,

284
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:14,150
why is it you again?

285
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:15,360
The Hainanese Chicken Rice

286
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:17,750
is the favorite staple food
of Shenjiang Industrial's boss.

287
00:14:17,750 --> 00:14:18,390
I'm telling you,

288
00:14:18,390 --> 00:14:19,840
this is a business banquet,

289
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,440
not a local feast in your hometown.

290
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:23,040
Change it back immediately.

291
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:24,550
Why can any kind of person

292
00:14:24,550 --> 00:14:26,390
boss around in my kitchen now?

293
00:14:26,910 --> 00:14:28,270
Who let this person in?

294
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:29,440
Kick her out!

295
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:30,000
Qiaoqi.

296
00:14:33,090 --> 00:14:34,030
Director Lu,

297
00:14:36,030 --> 00:14:37,320
the Hainanese Chicken Rice

298
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:39,250
was added temporarily at 5:00 p.m.

299
00:14:39,550 --> 00:14:40,870
Why is it no longer available?

300
00:14:40,870 --> 00:14:43,240
It's because the guests in the large
private room of the Chinese restaurant

301
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:46,580
are business owners from Guangdong's
new energy manufacturing sector.

302
00:14:46,580 --> 00:14:48,580
What do you expect our kitchen to do?

303
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,000
As for this bowl of

304
00:14:51,750 --> 00:14:54,940
plain noodles
in Fish Bone Soup with Bamboo Leaves,

305
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:57,360
you won't find it

306
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:58,960
at a typical hometown feast.

307
00:14:59,160 --> 00:15:00,640
The bamboo leaves are from

308
00:15:00,670 --> 00:15:02,480
Mount Emei in Sichuan.

309
00:15:02,870 --> 00:15:06,000
The fish bones come from
Pengze crucian carp in Jiangxi.

310
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:06,910
And these noodles

311
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:08,510
are fresh handmade noodles.

312
00:15:08,910 --> 00:15:11,440
Now you know how to
introduce it to the guests, right?

313
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:14,000
What are these nonsense words
you cobbled together?

314
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,460
Are you trying to bluff me?

315
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:17,510
I don't care what ingredients you use.

316
00:15:17,510 --> 00:15:18,630
If this noodle dish fails,

317
00:15:18,630 --> 00:15:20,360
will you take responsibility?

318
00:15:20,750 --> 00:15:21,440
I will.

319
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:28,520
Mr. Ji.

320
00:15:29,390 --> 00:15:30,390
Mr. Ji, I'm sorry.

321
00:15:30,560 --> 00:15:32,600
I was just too anxious.

322
00:15:36,510 --> 00:15:38,360
Director Lu, do me a favor.

323
00:15:43,870 --> 00:15:45,750
Should I take these noodles up?

324
00:15:48,550 --> 00:15:49,670
Put them on the cart.

325
00:15:49,670 --> 00:15:51,730
How could we let you serve the dishes?

326
00:16:06,840 --> 00:16:08,000
Not bad. Pretty good.

327
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:08,600
Glad you like it.

328
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:09,330
Pretty good.

329
00:16:10,990 --> 00:16:12,650
Marcos, let me introduce you.

330
00:16:14,060 --> 00:16:16,360
This is the executive chef
in charge of tonight's dinner,

331
00:16:16,360 --> 00:16:17,510
Chef Li Qiaoqi.

332
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:18,750
Marcos.

333
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:19,790
Mr. Cheng.

334
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:20,790
-Hello, Chef Li.
-Hello.

335
00:16:20,790 --> 00:16:22,870
Hello. I didn't expect you to be so young.

336
00:16:22,870 --> 00:16:24,540
Chef, let me tell you,

337
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:26,160
I am really satisfied

338
00:16:26,320 --> 00:16:27,750
with tonight's dinner.

339
00:16:30,360 --> 00:16:31,600
Mr. Cheng even said

340
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:32,790
he must see for himself

341
00:16:32,790 --> 00:16:34,390
such an amazing chef like you.

342
00:16:34,390 --> 00:16:35,000
Also,

343
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:36,150
I want to

344
00:16:36,150 --> 00:16:38,280
express my gratitude to you in person.

345
00:16:38,390 --> 00:16:39,390
Thank you for your hard work.

346
00:16:39,390 --> 00:16:41,510
The praise from Mr. Marcos and Mr. Cheng

347
00:16:41,510 --> 00:16:42,440
is our honor.

348
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:44,000
Actually, in Purong,

349
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,720
there are many chefs like me.

350
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,000
Thank you all.

351
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,720
Thank you for your hard work.

352
00:16:54,990 --> 00:16:55,720
This lady...

353
00:16:56,820 --> 00:16:58,060
My butler?

354
00:17:00,150 --> 00:17:01,590
Hello, Mr. Marcos.

355
00:17:01,910 --> 00:17:02,550
Actually,

356
00:17:02,870 --> 00:17:03,750
your butler is also

357
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:05,569
a very excellent chef.

358
00:17:05,849 --> 00:17:08,210
Today's plain noodles are made by her.

359
00:17:08,790 --> 00:17:12,150
I really finished that bowl
of plain noodles.

360
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:14,550
What a surprise, Ms. Xu.

361
00:17:14,550 --> 00:17:16,810
I didn't expect you
to be such a good cook.

362
00:17:17,310 --> 00:17:17,859
Well,

363
00:17:18,400 --> 00:17:19,400
can I

364
00:17:19,510 --> 00:17:22,400
order the plain noodles now

365
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:23,930
for my breakfast tomorrow?

366
00:17:24,109 --> 00:17:25,270
My pleasure.

367
00:17:25,839 --> 00:17:27,440
Then I want to order a bowl too.

368
00:17:27,440 --> 00:17:28,790
I will come here specifically tomorrow

369
00:17:28,790 --> 00:17:30,320
to have this for breakfast.

370
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:31,430
No problem.

371
00:17:32,110 --> 00:17:33,840
Let's add each other on WeChat.

372
00:17:34,790 --> 00:17:35,570
Well,

373
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:37,440
I think the food here
tastes really good.

374
00:17:37,440 --> 00:17:38,550
The most important thing is the broth.

375
00:17:38,550 --> 00:17:39,830
It's hard to make.

376
00:17:39,830 --> 00:17:41,630
That broth is really delicious.

377
00:17:56,440 --> 00:17:57,640
They are back.

378
00:18:06,270 --> 00:18:07,860
Awesome.

379
00:18:15,590 --> 00:18:16,460
Good job, everyone.

380
00:18:16,460 --> 00:18:17,370
You did great.

381
00:18:18,790 --> 00:18:21,390
We finally got through
this without a hitch.

382
00:18:21,830 --> 00:18:23,510
Even though Chef Jia

383
00:18:23,510 --> 00:18:25,110
disappeared without a word,

384
00:18:25,350 --> 00:18:27,680
our Chinese restaurant won't disappear.

385
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:30,640
Chef Li Qiaoqi,

386
00:18:31,070 --> 00:18:31,750
starting tomorrow,

387
00:18:31,750 --> 00:18:35,010
you will be the acting
head chef of the Chinese restaurant.

388
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:45,210
Any objections?

389
00:18:45,590 --> 00:18:46,960
Feel free to raise them

390
00:18:46,990 --> 00:18:48,850
and we can discuss them together.

391
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:50,060
No objections.

392
00:18:55,510 --> 00:18:57,000
Since there are no objections,

393
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:58,480
please follow

394
00:18:58,640 --> 00:19:00,920
the new head chef

395
00:19:01,590 --> 00:19:02,590
and work together

396
00:19:02,830 --> 00:19:05,200
to keep our Chinese restaurant running.

397
00:19:05,590 --> 00:19:06,110
Okay?

398
00:19:06,110 --> 00:19:07,350
Okay!

399
00:19:16,540 --> 00:19:18,030
Good. Thanks for your hard work.

400
00:19:18,030 --> 00:19:19,400
Wrap up your work,

401
00:19:19,400 --> 00:19:20,440
and go rest early.

402
00:19:20,440 --> 00:19:21,070
Okay.

403
00:19:22,960 --> 00:19:24,060
Thanks.

404
00:19:24,310 --> 00:19:25,030
Thanks.

405
00:19:27,030 --> 00:19:28,070
I didn't expect this at all.

406
00:19:28,070 --> 00:19:29,310
You are the best.

407
00:19:30,070 --> 00:19:31,400
You must be exhausted today too.

408
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:32,640
I'm fine.

409
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:34,440
Thanks for your help.

410
00:19:35,590 --> 00:19:36,750
I have something else to do.

411
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:37,680
I'll get going.

412
00:19:40,440 --> 00:19:41,030
Qiaoqi.

413
00:19:42,350 --> 00:19:43,010
I made this.

414
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:43,790
Try it.

415
00:19:46,590 --> 00:19:49,120
Eunuch Xue, are you
bribing the new head chef?

416
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:51,170
How am I like a eunuch?

417
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:52,550
What kind of nickname is that?

418
00:19:52,550 --> 00:19:54,350
You're biting the hand that feeds you.

419
00:19:54,350 --> 00:19:55,510
Eat it while it's hot.

420
00:19:55,510 --> 00:19:56,200
Thank you.

421
00:19:56,830 --> 00:19:58,290
I'll get back to work then.

422
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:04,070
Eunuch Xue? How do I look like a eunuch?

423
00:20:04,070 --> 00:20:04,830
What?

424
00:20:06,550 --> 00:20:08,920
The Chinese restaurant found
a new head chef so quickly?

425
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:10,510
She was promoted from the original

426
00:20:10,510 --> 00:20:11,310
sous-chefs of the Chinese restaurant.

427
00:20:11,310 --> 00:20:14,440
She was set to become head chef
after tonight's banquet.

428
00:20:14,790 --> 00:20:16,400
Didn't Jia Shikun tell me

429
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:18,350
that everyone in the Chinese restaurant
except him is useless

430
00:20:18,350 --> 00:20:19,440
and can't accomplish anything?

431
00:20:19,440 --> 00:20:20,030
Then...

432
00:20:22,300 --> 00:20:23,760
What's wrong with Ji Feng?

433
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:25,400
Is he just grasping at straws?

434
00:20:25,400 --> 00:20:26,350
Or is it that

435
00:20:26,920 --> 00:20:28,980
Jia Shikun is completely lying to me?

436
00:20:30,030 --> 00:20:32,090
That won't do. I have to go take a look.

437
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:52,290
Isn't this Mr. Duan Jr.?

438
00:20:52,550 --> 00:20:54,850
What brings you down to our kitchen?

439
00:20:54,980 --> 00:20:58,160
So, where's your new head chef?

440
00:20:58,160 --> 00:20:59,620
Why are you looking for me?

441
00:21:01,880 --> 00:21:02,750
It's you?

442
00:21:04,350 --> 00:21:05,510
Can't it be me?

443
00:21:05,590 --> 00:21:06,990
You're on Ji Feng's side?

444
00:21:07,640 --> 00:21:09,840
Whoever promotes me,
I'm on their side.

445
00:21:10,550 --> 00:21:11,480
What do you want?

446
00:21:15,280 --> 00:21:16,880
How much does Ji Feng pay you?

447
00:21:16,990 --> 00:21:18,090
I'll double it.

448
00:21:18,270 --> 00:21:19,130
Come to Kuanli,

449
00:21:19,440 --> 00:21:21,300
and you can still be the head chef.

450
00:21:22,350 --> 00:21:23,550
Why are you laughing?

451
00:21:24,310 --> 00:21:24,990
Nothing.

452
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:26,680
I just learned for the first time

453
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:29,460
that your head chefs
at Kuanli come in bulk.

454
00:21:30,070 --> 00:21:31,200
You think I'm lying?

455
00:21:32,880 --> 00:21:34,350
If I'm not mistaken,

456
00:21:34,510 --> 00:21:36,350
Jia Shikun was also lured to Kuanli

457
00:21:36,350 --> 00:21:37,590
by your words.

458
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:40,750
Mr. Duan Jr., I might lack backbone,

459
00:21:40,780 --> 00:21:43,100
but you don't have
to treat me like a fool.

460
00:21:49,510 --> 00:21:50,750
Don't be ungrateful.

461
00:21:54,070 --> 00:21:55,100
Sorry,

462
00:21:55,310 --> 00:21:56,550
I really plan

463
00:21:56,550 --> 00:21:58,400
to stay in Purong's kitchen.

464
00:21:58,590 --> 00:21:59,920
What can you do about it?

465
00:22:03,690 --> 00:22:05,340
[F&B Department, Li Qiaoqi]

466
00:22:04,030 --> 00:22:05,030
Li Qiaoqi, right?

467
00:22:06,790 --> 00:22:07,920
Let's see

468
00:22:07,920 --> 00:22:09,580
how big a storm you can stir up.

469
00:22:09,830 --> 00:22:10,890
Let's wait and see.

470
00:22:11,920 --> 00:22:13,680
Take care. I won't see you out.

471
00:22:40,270 --> 00:22:42,590
Mr. Yang, may I walk you
through tomorrow's schedule?

472
00:22:42,590 --> 00:22:44,030
Our hotel has prepared...

473
00:22:44,030 --> 00:22:44,830
Wait a minute.

474
00:22:49,440 --> 00:22:50,270
Hello?

475
00:22:51,100 --> 00:22:52,990
Ms. Xu, give me the room card.

476
00:22:53,270 --> 00:22:56,870
-What? What happened to my grandpa?
-I’ll go open the door.

477
00:23:10,740 --> 00:23:12,200
Mr. Yang, are you alright?

478
00:23:18,170 --> 00:23:20,300
My grandpa fell into a coma yesterday.

479
00:23:22,110 --> 00:23:24,710
He woke up today
and couldn't remember anyone.

480
00:23:28,110 --> 00:23:30,350
I want to rest early tonight.

481
00:23:31,820 --> 00:23:33,550
I understand. I'll arrange it.

482
00:23:34,590 --> 00:23:36,110
Thank you, Ms. Xu.

483
00:23:38,350 --> 00:23:40,720
Mr. Yang, the room is ready for you.

484
00:23:40,750 --> 00:23:42,810
I haven't finished what I was saying.

485
00:23:43,200 --> 00:23:44,200
Mr. Yang is tired.

486
00:23:44,350 --> 00:23:45,310
He wants to rest.

487
00:23:45,590 --> 00:23:46,880
I have important matters
to discuss with him.

488
00:23:46,880 --> 00:23:47,400
What do you know?

489
00:23:47,400 --> 00:23:48,680
You can talk to him about it tomorrow.

490
00:23:48,680 --> 00:23:49,920
Whatever it is,

491
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:51,600
we'll talk tomorrow.

492
00:23:52,920 --> 00:23:53,990
Okay.

493
00:23:54,200 --> 00:23:55,330
I won't disturb you.

494
00:23:55,510 --> 00:23:56,310
Good night.

495
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:04,080
Good night, Mr. Yang.

496
00:24:04,680 --> 00:24:05,400
Thank you.

497
00:24:15,980 --> 00:24:17,760
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

498
00:24:24,350 --> 00:24:26,680
[Marcos's grandfather attended
the youth architectural design program]

499
00:24:26,700 --> 00:24:29,210
[at Huiwen Yingzao in Shanghai, China.]

500
00:24:30,780 --> 00:24:32,440
[Marcos's grandfather attended
the youth architectural design program]

501
00:24:32,460 --> 00:24:34,200
[at Huiwen Yingzao in Shanghai, China.]

502
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:04,410
You've worked hard, honey,

503
00:25:04,830 --> 00:25:06,430
especially being pregnant.

504
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:08,400
Did the contract signing go smoothly?

505
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:09,590
Not yet,

506
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:10,880
but soon.

507
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:13,030
The boss had a great meal tonight.

508
00:25:13,310 --> 00:25:15,030
He said he was going
to eat somewhere else,

509
00:25:15,030 --> 00:25:16,030
but guess what?

510
00:25:16,350 --> 00:25:18,070
He ended up listening to me.

511
00:25:18,260 --> 00:25:19,550
The five-table banquet

512
00:25:19,550 --> 00:25:21,480
has been moved to our Purong Hotel.

513
00:25:23,690 --> 00:25:25,240
You are amazing, baby.

514
00:25:26,030 --> 00:25:27,790
But that Xu Miyu,

515
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:29,640
showing off everywhere

516
00:25:30,110 --> 00:25:32,110
and going against me in everything.

517
00:25:33,070 --> 00:25:34,310
She's so annoying.

518
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:37,310
Who are you talking about?

519
00:25:37,310 --> 00:25:38,450
Who else could it be?

520
00:25:38,790 --> 00:25:39,750
Your ex-wife.

521
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:40,880
If it weren't for her,

522
00:25:40,880 --> 00:25:43,080
I would have signed the contract today.

523
00:25:44,070 --> 00:25:45,400
She was the one who stopped me,

524
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:47,600
insisting that the boss needed to rest.

525
00:25:48,110 --> 00:25:49,350
Why is she like this?

526
00:25:56,350 --> 00:25:56,920
I think she must

527
00:25:56,920 --> 00:25:58,030
hate me.

528
00:25:58,510 --> 00:26:01,350
She's trying everything
to exact personal revenge.

529
00:26:01,350 --> 00:26:03,350
I can't be bothered to deal with her.

530
00:26:03,640 --> 00:26:06,070
Anyway, I'll go see the boss
first thing tomorrow morning,

531
00:26:06,070 --> 00:26:07,270
to press my advantage

532
00:26:07,510 --> 00:26:09,840
and make sure to get this contract signed.

533
00:26:10,270 --> 00:26:10,590
Otherwise,

534
00:26:10,590 --> 00:26:11,920
all my hard work over the past 2 days

535
00:26:11,920 --> 00:26:13,310
will be in vain.

536
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:16,800
Right.

537
00:26:17,880 --> 00:26:20,110
You can definitely
get the contract signed.

538
00:26:20,110 --> 00:26:21,170
I have faith in you.

539
00:26:23,310 --> 00:26:23,970
Go to sleep.

540
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:27,010
I have to work early tomorrow morning.

541
00:26:42,350 --> 00:26:44,110
What's wrong with me like this now?

542
00:26:44,110 --> 00:26:46,170
I make my own money to support myself.

543
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:49,530
Is it any more shameful
than being your full-time nanny?

544
00:27:10,310 --> 00:27:11,440
Hello, Director Lu.

545
00:27:18,550 --> 00:27:19,880
Mr. Yang's flight has been rescheduled.

546
00:27:19,880 --> 00:27:22,740
We are arranging a car
to take him to the airport now.

547
00:27:23,110 --> 00:27:23,640
Ms. Lu.

548
00:27:23,640 --> 00:27:25,700
Thank you for your warm hospitality.

549
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:28,350
Mr. Yang.

550
00:27:29,070 --> 00:27:30,550
Regarding the cooperation agreement

551
00:27:30,550 --> 00:27:31,440
we discussed at the last banquet,

552
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:33,040
have you made a decision yet?

553
00:27:33,200 --> 00:27:35,720
I have an emergency
and need to leave China now.

554
00:27:35,720 --> 00:27:37,720
Let's discuss our cooperation later.

555
00:27:37,720 --> 00:27:39,650
Thank you for your understanding.

556
00:27:39,690 --> 00:27:41,090
Of course, I understand.

557
00:27:41,640 --> 00:27:43,510
I wonder if you could

558
00:27:43,750 --> 00:27:45,880
reach a letter of intent with us first.

559
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:48,510
Even a verbal agreement would do.

560
00:27:48,510 --> 00:27:50,960
It would show
your recognition of our services.

561
00:27:50,960 --> 00:27:52,960
Purong Hotel has a great reputation.

562
00:27:52,960 --> 00:27:54,110
There's no need to rush.

563
00:27:54,110 --> 00:27:56,440
Besides, long-term cooperation
is not a trifling matter.

564
00:27:56,440 --> 00:27:59,350
I think we should sit down
and talk this through sometime.

565
00:27:59,350 --> 00:28:00,750
When exactly is that?

566
00:28:01,680 --> 00:28:03,110
That depends on you.

567
00:28:03,590 --> 00:28:04,790
If your hotel

568
00:28:05,160 --> 00:28:07,560
can maintain excellent service as always,

569
00:28:08,020 --> 00:28:09,310
then when I'll visit

570
00:28:09,470 --> 00:28:12,370
and whether we cooperate
is just a matter of time.

571
00:28:14,110 --> 00:28:14,750
Yes.

572
00:28:18,440 --> 00:28:20,900
Ms. Lu, are you coming
to the airport with us?

573
00:28:21,310 --> 00:28:22,350
I won't be going.

574
00:28:22,350 --> 00:28:23,610
I have a meeting later,

575
00:28:23,750 --> 00:28:26,150
so I'll leave it to you
to see him off, Ms. Xu.

576
00:28:28,800 --> 00:28:30,260
Have a safe trip, Mr. Yang.

577
00:28:30,550 --> 00:28:32,430
Welcome back to Purong Hotel.

578
00:28:32,430 --> 00:28:33,070
Thank you.

579
00:28:48,430 --> 00:28:49,630
-Please.
-Thank you.

580
00:28:54,600 --> 00:28:55,500
Mr. Marcos,

581
00:28:55,520 --> 00:28:56,850
your flight is delayed.

582
00:28:57,230 --> 00:28:58,010
How long is the delay?

583
00:28:58,010 --> 00:28:59,270
Four hours.

584
00:28:59,310 --> 00:29:00,070
Four ho...

585
00:29:02,050 --> 00:29:04,650
See if there are
any other places you want to go.

586
00:29:05,950 --> 00:29:06,710
Whatever.

587
00:29:07,810 --> 00:29:09,330
Can I arrange it then?

588
00:29:16,080 --> 00:29:18,140
Let's go to East Changzhi Road first.

589
00:29:25,720 --> 00:29:29,380
This is the Huiwen Architectural Design
and Research Institute.

590
00:29:30,350 --> 00:29:31,750
Its predecessor

591
00:29:31,770 --> 00:29:34,330
was Huiwen Yingzao, built in 1942.

592
00:29:35,440 --> 00:29:37,510
At that time, in addition to
producing a large number

593
00:29:37,510 --> 00:29:39,420
of exquisite architectural designs,

594
00:29:39,420 --> 00:29:41,720
a large group of outstanding

595
00:29:41,720 --> 00:29:43,920
foreign design masters also came here.

596
00:29:44,920 --> 00:29:46,000
They set up

597
00:29:46,000 --> 00:29:48,480
a youth architectural design program here,

598
00:29:48,680 --> 00:29:50,880
cultivating a group of

599
00:29:50,880 --> 00:29:53,720
rare and excellent
architectural design talents for China.

600
00:29:53,720 --> 00:29:54,830
This story

601
00:29:54,830 --> 00:29:56,110
is a fine example,

602
00:29:56,110 --> 00:29:59,070
both in terms of cultural exchange

603
00:29:59,070 --> 00:30:00,680
between China and the world

604
00:30:00,750 --> 00:30:02,590
and in the field of architectural design.

605
00:30:02,590 --> 00:30:03,350
These are some photographs

606
00:30:03,350 --> 00:30:05,720
from Huiwen Yingzao,
including a few group photos

607
00:30:05,720 --> 00:30:06,680
from that time.

608
00:30:09,810 --> 00:30:10,640
Ms. Xu,

609
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:15,000
the one on the far left of the second row

610
00:30:15,320 --> 00:30:16,380
is my grandfather.

611
00:30:18,720 --> 00:30:20,830
If only he were here too.

612
00:30:22,110 --> 00:30:25,180
Do you want to call your grandfather then?

613
00:30:31,070 --> 00:30:32,550
Will he still remember me?

614
00:30:32,680 --> 00:30:34,540
How will you know if you don't try?

615
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:41,980
Mr. Yang Siyuan, you have a phone call.

616
00:30:43,270 --> 00:30:44,030
Grandpa.

617
00:30:44,590 --> 00:30:46,450
You have the wrong number, child.

618
00:30:48,160 --> 00:30:49,350
I am in China.

619
00:30:49,350 --> 00:30:51,240
In Shanghai, China.

620
00:30:51,790 --> 00:30:52,590
I'm looking at

621
00:30:54,690 --> 00:30:56,400
your pictures when you were young.

622
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:58,830
At Huiwen Yingzao, see?

623
00:31:06,790 --> 00:31:07,880
This is Wang.

624
00:31:09,310 --> 00:31:10,330
Li.

625
00:31:11,440 --> 00:31:12,690
This is our monitor.

626
00:31:15,590 --> 00:31:16,880
You still remember them?

627
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:18,440
More than remember,

628
00:31:18,550 --> 00:31:20,270
I miss them to death.

629
00:31:20,930 --> 00:31:22,710
Huiwen Yingzao.

630
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:24,550
Shanghai, China.

631
00:31:24,880 --> 00:31:26,610
The place where I once studied.

632
00:31:26,830 --> 00:31:27,510
Yes.

633
00:31:30,510 --> 00:31:31,070
Grandpa.

634
00:31:34,790 --> 00:31:35,790
Grandpa, then...

635
00:31:37,830 --> 00:31:38,790
Then I am...

636
00:31:39,240 --> 00:31:39,880
You...

637
00:31:40,170 --> 00:31:41,870
Aren't you my Marcos?

638
00:31:42,110 --> 00:31:42,830
Come here quickly.

639
00:31:42,830 --> 00:31:43,880
I miss you.

640
00:31:45,970 --> 00:31:47,490
I miss you very much too.

641
00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:50,480
My flight arrives tomorrow,

642
00:31:50,590 --> 00:31:52,520
then I will go see you immediately.

643
00:31:52,830 --> 00:31:53,890
Come over quickly.

644
00:31:54,310 --> 00:31:55,310
I'll wait for you.

645
00:31:56,310 --> 00:31:57,310
See you tomorrow.

646
00:31:57,350 --> 00:31:58,280
I'll hang up now.

647
00:32:10,070 --> 00:32:10,880
Time flies,

648
00:32:10,880 --> 00:32:13,590
but beautiful memories last forever.

649
00:32:13,920 --> 00:32:16,950
Let me take a picture
of you with your grandpa's photo.

650
00:32:17,110 --> 00:32:17,920
Can you?

651
00:32:20,070 --> 00:32:20,790
Come.

652
00:32:25,350 --> 00:32:26,750
One, two, three.

653
00:32:30,680 --> 00:32:31,510
Thank you.

654
00:32:38,110 --> 00:32:38,920
Ms. Xu.

655
00:32:40,310 --> 00:32:41,310
Can I have a hug?

656
00:32:41,440 --> 00:32:42,350
Of course.

657
00:32:49,310 --> 00:32:50,070
Thank you.

658
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:52,750
You know what?

659
00:32:54,070 --> 00:32:54,750
You...

660
00:32:57,110 --> 00:32:58,170
You know what, I...

661
00:32:59,410 --> 00:33:01,310
You are the most considerate
hotel attendant

662
00:33:01,310 --> 00:33:04,070
I have ever met traveling the world.

663
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:05,830
You make me feel

664
00:33:06,830 --> 00:33:08,510
especially secure.

665
00:33:08,590 --> 00:33:11,310
It feels very much like coming home.

666
00:33:12,440 --> 00:33:13,900
Thank you for saying that.

667
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:16,090
Then,

668
00:33:16,550 --> 00:33:19,750
you are welcome to visit
Purong Hotel often in the future.

669
00:33:19,860 --> 00:33:21,290
Coming often is a must.

670
00:33:22,140 --> 00:33:24,390
And I will let all my staff

671
00:33:24,590 --> 00:33:25,680
come and

672
00:33:25,970 --> 00:33:27,920
enjoy the service here.

673
00:33:27,920 --> 00:33:30,520
We will definitely
serve you wholeheartedly.

674
00:33:31,680 --> 00:33:32,550
Okay.

675
00:33:33,350 --> 00:33:35,070
It should be about time.

676
00:33:35,240 --> 00:33:36,900
Let me take you to the airport.

677
00:33:37,440 --> 00:33:38,510
Great, let's go.

678
00:33:38,720 --> 00:33:39,720
This way, please.

679
00:33:52,810 --> 00:33:53,990
[Unread]

680
00:33:53,990 --> 00:33:56,820
[Unread]

681
00:33:56,950 --> 00:33:57,820
[Loading]

682
00:33:59,530 --> 00:34:01,740
[From: CBO Marcos Yang]

683
00:34:02,510 --> 00:34:03,160
It's done.

684
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:04,440
What's done?

685
00:34:04,510 --> 00:34:07,070
Marcos wants to sign
a long-term contract with us.

686
00:34:07,070 --> 00:34:08,760
This is all so sudden.

687
00:34:09,710 --> 00:34:11,440
I heard gossip from the front desk

688
00:34:11,440 --> 00:34:12,440
that he's very hard to deal with.

689
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:14,070
He seems pleasant on the outside,

690
00:34:14,070 --> 00:34:15,960
but is as solid as a rock on the inside.

691
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:17,420
I thought we had no chance.

692
00:34:18,550 --> 00:34:19,350
Secretary Wu,

693
00:34:19,400 --> 00:34:21,440
notify the management to hold a meeting

694
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:22,440
in an hour,

695
00:34:22,590 --> 00:34:25,190
after Director Lu
comes back from the airport.

696
00:34:25,350 --> 00:34:25,830
Okay.

697
00:34:36,670 --> 00:34:37,400
You're here.

698
00:34:37,550 --> 00:34:38,440
Talk to you later.

699
00:34:38,440 --> 00:34:38,960
Okay.

700
00:34:52,110 --> 00:34:54,280
Our hosting of Liberty Group this time

701
00:34:54,840 --> 00:34:55,880
was very successful.

702
00:34:55,880 --> 00:34:57,920
They have verbally promised

703
00:34:58,110 --> 00:34:59,960
a long-term contract with us.

704
00:35:00,630 --> 00:35:02,670
All processes are moving forward.

705
00:35:09,880 --> 00:35:12,190
The sales department has made
such a great contribution this time.

706
00:35:12,190 --> 00:35:13,150
We should thank

707
00:35:13,920 --> 00:35:15,590
Mr. Qian for his strong support.

708
00:35:15,590 --> 00:35:16,920
You are too kind, Mr. Ji.

709
00:35:17,440 --> 00:35:18,880
This time, our sales department

710
00:35:18,880 --> 00:35:19,920
is honored

711
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:21,050
to fight side by side

712
00:35:21,550 --> 00:35:23,710
with Mr. Ji.

713
00:35:32,510 --> 00:35:34,110
This time, Director Lu

714
00:35:34,110 --> 00:35:34,920
has secured such an important client

715
00:35:34,920 --> 00:35:36,630
for our hotel.

716
00:35:36,880 --> 00:35:38,360
It demonstrated our strength externally

717
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:40,710
and boosted our morale internally.

718
00:35:41,320 --> 00:35:44,480
Although Director Lu
just got transferred here,

719
00:35:45,110 --> 00:35:47,280
her performance has been outstanding.

720
00:35:47,280 --> 00:35:49,690
After discussing with Mr. Qian,

721
00:35:49,880 --> 00:35:50,710
I announce

722
00:35:51,230 --> 00:35:52,710
that Lu Zhenzhen

723
00:35:52,710 --> 00:35:55,000
is promoted to VIP Account Manager.

724
00:36:01,230 --> 00:36:04,190
Ms. Lu, you'll take the lead

725
00:36:04,760 --> 00:36:06,110
on the follow-up with Liberty Group.

726
00:36:06,110 --> 00:36:06,710
Yes.

727
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:17,070
[Changzhi Road]

728
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:23,420
Sir, I'll get off here.

729
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:39,230
Next is

730
00:36:40,440 --> 00:36:41,640
the HSKP Department.

731
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:42,550
Well,

732
00:36:43,110 --> 00:36:43,710
Mr. Ji,

733
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:47,110
our HSKP Department's
performance this time

734
00:36:47,110 --> 00:36:50,110
indeed fell short of
the standard of a five-star hotel.

735
00:36:50,110 --> 00:36:51,920
As the leader in charge,

736
00:36:51,940 --> 00:36:52,730
first of all,

737
00:36:53,000 --> 00:36:54,110
I need to make a self-criticism.

738
00:36:54,110 --> 00:36:55,920
It's my fault for
choosing the wrong person.

739
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:58,440
The executive floor forewoman Xu Miyu

740
00:36:58,440 --> 00:37:00,440
neglected her duty

741
00:37:00,440 --> 00:37:02,030
while receiving VIP guests.

742
00:37:02,030 --> 00:37:02,920
It almost

743
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:04,560
caused a major accident,

744
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:05,800
bringing irreversible losses

745
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:07,960
to the hotel.

746
00:37:08,190 --> 00:37:08,760
She is...

747
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:12,100
Xu Miyu.

748
00:37:12,510 --> 00:37:14,070
So you still know how to show up.

749
00:37:14,070 --> 00:37:15,800
You made mistakes at work

750
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:16,760
and are late for the meeting.

751
00:37:16,760 --> 00:37:18,160
What are you trying to do?

752
00:37:19,280 --> 00:37:21,030
Do you still respect me as your leader?

753
00:37:21,030 --> 00:37:23,590
Do you even care about
the hotel's work discipline?

754
00:37:23,590 --> 00:37:25,440
Do you think just
because you're a forewoman

755
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:27,150
you can completely disregard us

756
00:37:27,150 --> 00:37:28,320
managers?

757
00:37:28,800 --> 00:37:29,830
No, Mr. Feng.

758
00:37:29,860 --> 00:37:31,710
I was taking a guest to the airport,

759
00:37:31,710 --> 00:37:33,190
and the traffic was
a bit heavy on the way back.

760
00:37:33,190 --> 00:37:34,440
-I'm sorry.
-Look.

761
00:37:34,440 --> 00:37:35,880
Still making excuses.

762
00:37:36,300 --> 00:37:38,360
You blame the traffic
for being late to the meeting.

763
00:37:38,360 --> 00:37:41,440
You forgot the VIP's allergies,

764
00:37:41,460 --> 00:37:43,440
and you blamed others for not telling you.

765
00:37:43,440 --> 00:37:45,760
If all of us were like you,

766
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:47,190
shirking responsibility

767
00:37:47,190 --> 00:37:48,760
whenever there's a problem,

768
00:37:48,760 --> 00:37:50,290
how would any work get done?

769
00:37:50,440 --> 00:37:51,320
Ms. Xu.

770
00:37:51,920 --> 00:37:55,120
The executive floor
will be ruined by you sooner or later.

771
00:37:59,260 --> 00:38:00,010
Mr. Ji.

772
00:38:01,630 --> 00:38:02,400
I'm sorry.

773
00:38:03,400 --> 00:38:04,570
Our HSKP Department

774
00:38:04,760 --> 00:38:07,230
made such a huge mistake

775
00:38:07,230 --> 00:38:09,090
in this important VIP reception.

776
00:38:09,190 --> 00:38:10,340
I take full responsibility.

777
00:38:10,340 --> 00:38:13,080
I didn't discipline this subordinate well,

778
00:38:13,360 --> 00:38:14,650
and I can't shirk the blame.

779
00:38:14,650 --> 00:38:15,740
Please punish me.

780
00:38:20,040 --> 00:38:21,010
Mr. Feng,

781
00:38:21,670 --> 00:38:23,800
don't be in a hurry to ask for punishment.

782
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:24,930
Let me finish first.

783
00:38:26,320 --> 00:38:28,670
During the HSKP Department's
VIP reception,

784
00:38:28,670 --> 00:38:31,030
there were some mistakes at first.

785
00:38:32,400 --> 00:38:33,800
But fortunately,

786
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:36,400
the forewoman and staff
on the executive floor

787
00:38:36,400 --> 00:38:37,890
later

788
00:38:37,960 --> 00:38:39,160
observed carefully,

789
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:40,590
found the problems in time,

790
00:38:40,590 --> 00:38:42,070
and quickly adjusted themselves

791
00:38:42,070 --> 00:38:43,590
to improve the service quality.

792
00:38:43,590 --> 00:38:45,790
In the end, with high-quality service,

793
00:38:45,800 --> 00:38:48,070
they cooperated with
the F&B and sales departments

794
00:38:48,070 --> 00:38:49,320
and successfully completed

795
00:38:49,320 --> 00:38:50,520
this reception task.

796
00:38:50,840 --> 00:38:52,590
Their performance was commendable.

797
00:38:52,590 --> 00:38:53,070
But as for

798
00:38:53,070 --> 00:38:54,590
the cause of the series of accidents

799
00:38:54,590 --> 00:38:56,150
in the HSKP Department,

800
00:38:56,360 --> 00:38:57,590
investigation shows that

801
00:38:57,590 --> 00:39:00,070
they were caused by a handover accident

802
00:39:00,630 --> 00:39:02,320
during the transfer of documents.

803
00:39:02,320 --> 00:39:03,040
Mr. Feng,

804
00:39:04,320 --> 00:39:06,120
do you have anything to explain?

805
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:09,570
Well,

806
00:39:10,440 --> 00:39:10,920
well...

807
00:39:10,920 --> 00:39:12,150
As for

808
00:39:12,150 --> 00:39:14,080
the shampoo reselling by our staff

809
00:39:14,440 --> 00:39:16,250
and the linen scandal,

810
00:39:16,480 --> 00:39:17,550
our investigation shows

811
00:39:17,550 --> 00:39:19,110
that you were behind both, Mr. Feng—

812
00:39:19,110 --> 00:39:20,150
stealing from the hotel

813
00:39:20,150 --> 00:39:21,480
and lining your own pockets.

814
00:39:21,480 --> 00:39:23,080
The evidence is conclusive.

815
00:39:23,400 --> 00:39:25,390
In addition, the GM's Office

816
00:39:25,590 --> 00:39:27,320
has recently evaluated the abilities

817
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:28,850
of all department leaders.

818
00:39:29,400 --> 00:39:31,530
Mr. Feng failed to meet the standards.

819
00:39:33,710 --> 00:39:35,230
Based on the above points

820
00:39:35,230 --> 00:39:37,430
and the hotel management regulations,

821
00:39:37,960 --> 00:39:38,960
I hereby announce

822
00:39:39,550 --> 00:39:42,150
that Mr. Feng is dismissed.

823
00:39:46,740 --> 00:39:48,140
You can't fire me.

824
00:39:48,760 --> 00:39:49,360
Mr. Ji,

825
00:39:50,150 --> 00:39:53,190
Mr. Feng is the head
of HSKP Department after all.

826
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:54,760
You made the decision

827
00:39:55,440 --> 00:39:57,920
to fire him all by yourself?

828
00:39:58,110 --> 00:39:59,840
Isn't that a bit too hasty?

829
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:00,440
Exactly.

830
00:40:00,810 --> 00:40:02,480
At the very least, you should

831
00:40:02,500 --> 00:40:04,160
discuss it with Mr. Wei first.

832
00:40:04,230 --> 00:40:05,630
So what you're saying is,

833
00:40:05,880 --> 00:40:07,030
the hotel's general manager

834
00:40:07,030 --> 00:40:09,590
can't make personnel
decisions independently?

